rows.label: qst701711_msg0001
rows.name: Kgh...

rows.label: qst701711_msg0002
rows.name: That's enough. Stop.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm grateful for your
feelings, but I have an
obligation to be killed by him.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0004
rows.name: What's that? Are you stupid?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0005
rows.name:
It means I can only atone this way.
What I did was so terrible...

rows.label: qst701711_msg0006
rows.name: ...Hey, you said atonement, didn't you?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0007
rows.name:
Isn't that about the help you've
been giving people without
receiving proper compensation?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0008
rows.name:
...I know it's not nearly
enough. That's why...

rows.label: qst701711_msg0009
rows.name:
Don't you dare say you'll make
up for it by dying. My sister
would be even sadder!!

rows.label: qst701711_msg0010
rows.name:
You want to die because you want to
be at ease. You just want to bask
in the feeling of having atoned!

rows.label: qst701711_msg0012
rows.name:
I don't care whether you live
or die, but I won't let you
waste my sister's feelings.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0013
rows.name:
Stop being so self-absorbed.
When you've cooled your head,
we'll have a strategy meeting.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0014
rows.name: Huh? For what?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0015
rows.name:
We're going to crush the Bloody
Lobsters! We are!! So that we can
start a new life from now on!!!

rows.label: qst701711_msg0016
rows.name:
I can't do anything about them
by myself. If you have free time,
help me and atone, you idiot.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0017
rows.name:
Haha, why does it have to be
like this... It's absurd.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0018
rows.name:
Why are you siblings, you and
your sister, so alike...

rows.label: qst701711_msg0019
rows.name: Is the brawl over, mo?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0020
rows.name:
I was worried and came to
see, mo. What happened, mo?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0021
rows.name: Um, there were various circumstances.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0022
rows.name:
I'm sorry for the disturbance.
It's all right now...

rows.label: qst701711_msg0023
rows.name:
A past you want to redo,
huh? Why are we so bound
by this thing called fate?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0024
rows.name: ...I've been curious for a while.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0025
rows.name:
Is your detached way of thinking
related to you becoming a Man-Eater?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0026
rows.name:
You're unusually sharp. Have
you taken an interest?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0027
rows.name: I was just curious as a fellow Blade.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0028
rows.name:
Don't. You'll just become
a half-wit. Like me.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0029
rows.name: ...Is that really so?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0030
rows.name:
There's no need to be so certain. At the very
least, if the person has made a choice and
decided not to regret it, that's another story.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0031
rows.name: ...Shin?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0032
rows.name:
If you think of yourself as a half-wit,
you become one. You should just think of
it as getting the best of both worlds.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0033
rows.name: Why are you so positive?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0034
rows.name:
If you want to move forward, you
have to look forward, don't you?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0035
rows.name:
Honestly... Being with you all makes
me feel like I'm losing my mind.
